title: World Empanadas
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Take-out, Mexican, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A unique concept restaurant. Vegan empanadas include quinoa & lentils, pinto bean & rice and sometimes a daily special such as a soy chorizo empanada. Also has a vegan tortilla soup. Mild, medium, and spicy salsas are offered. The owner/manager is friendly and the space is quaint with a few tables and chairs outside as well.
